var book = {
	"name": "1 Timothy",
	"numChapters": 6,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Paul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29681A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29681A\"></sup>an apostle of Christ Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29681B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29681B\"></sup>by command of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29681C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29681C\"></sup>God our Savior and of Christ Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29681D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29681D\"></sup>our hope,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>To Timothy, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29682E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29682E\"></sup>my true child in the faith:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29682F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29682F\"></sup>Grace, mercy, and peace from God the Father and Christ Jesus our Lord.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29683G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29683G\"></sup>As I urged you when I was going to Macedonia, remain at Ephesus so that you may charge certain persons not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29683H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29683H\"></sup>to teach any different doctrine,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29684I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29684I\"></sup>to devote themselves to myths and endless <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29684J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29684J\"></sup>genealogies, which promote <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29684K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29684K\"></sup>speculations rather than the stewardship from God that is by faith.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The aim of our charge is love <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29685L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29685L\"></sup>that issues from a pure heart and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29685M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29685M\"></sup>a good conscience and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29685N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29685N\"></sup>a sincere faith.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Certain persons, by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29686O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29686O\"></sup>swerving from these, have wandered away into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29686P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29686P\"></sup>vain discussion,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>desiring to be teachers of the law, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29687Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29687Q\"></sup>without understanding either what they are saying or the things about which they make confident assertions.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Now we know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29688R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29688R\"></sup>the law is good, if one uses it lawfully,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>understanding this, that the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29689S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29689S\"></sup>law is not laid down for the just but for the lawless and disobedient, for the ungodly and sinners, for the unholy and profane, for those who strike their fathers and mothers, for murderers,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>the sexually immoral, men who practice homosexuality, enslavers, liars, perjurers, and whatever else is contrary to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29690T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29690T\"></sup>sound doctrine,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>in accordance with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29691U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29691U\"></sup>the gospel of the glory of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29691V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29691V\"></sup>the blessed God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29691W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29691W\"></sup>with which I have been entrusted.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I thank him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29692X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29692X\"></sup>who has given me strength, Christ Jesus our Lord, because he judged me faithful, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29692Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29692Y\"></sup>appointing me to his service,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>though formerly I was a blasphemer, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29693Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29693Z\"></sup>persecutor, and insolent opponent. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29693AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29693AA\"></sup>I received mercy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29693AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29693AB\"></sup>because I had acted ignorantly in unbelief,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29694AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29694AC\"></sup>the grace of our Lord overflowed for me with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29694AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29694AD\"></sup>faith and love that are in Christ Jesus.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The saying is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29695AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29695AE\"></sup>trustworthy and deserving of full acceptance, that Christ Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29695AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29695AF\"></sup>came into the world to save sinners, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29695AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29695AG\"></sup>of whom I am the foremost.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But I received mercy for this reason, that in me, as the foremost, Jesus Christ might display his perfect patience as an example to those who were to believe in him for eternal life.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29697AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29697AH\"></sup>the King of the ages, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29697AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29697AI\"></sup>immortal, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29697AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29697AJ\"></sup>invisible, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29697AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29697AK\"></sup>the only God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29697AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29697AL\"></sup>be honor and glory forever and ever. Amen.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>This charge <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29698AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29698AM\"></sup>I entrust to you, Timothy, my child, in accordance with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29698AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29698AN\"></sup>the prophecies previously made about you, that by them you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29698AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29698AO\"></sup>wage the good warfare,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29699AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29699AP\"></sup>holding faith and a good conscience. By rejecting this, some have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29699AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29699AQ\"></sup>made shipwreck of their faith,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>among whom are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29700AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29700AR\"></sup>Hymenaeus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29700AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29700AS\"></sup>Alexander, whom I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29700AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29700AT\"></sup>have handed over to Satan that they may learn not to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29700AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29700AU\"></sup>blaspheme."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>First of all, then, I urge that supplications, prayers, intercessions, and thanksgivings be made for all people,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29702A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29702A\"></sup>for kings and all who are in high positions, that we may lead a peaceful and quiet life, godly and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29702B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29702B\"></sup>dignified in every way.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>This is good, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29703C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29703C\"></sup>it is pleasing in the sight of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29703D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29703D\"></sup>God our Savior,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>who desires <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29704E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29704E\"></sup>all people to be saved and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29704F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29704F\"></sup>to come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29704G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29704G\"></sup>the knowledge of the truth.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29705H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29705H\"></sup>there is one God, and there is one mediator between God and men, the man Christ Jesus,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29706I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29706I\"></sup>who gave himself as a ransom for all, which is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29706J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29706J\"></sup>the testimony given <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29706K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29706K\"></sup>at the proper time.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29707L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29707L\"></sup>For this I was appointed a preacher and an apostle (<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29707M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29707M\"></sup>I am telling the truth, I am not lying), <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29707N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29707N\"></sup>a teacher of the Gentiles in faith and truth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I desire then that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29708O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29708O\"></sup>in every place the men should pray, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29708P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29708P\"></sup>lifting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29708Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29708Q\"></sup>holy hands without anger or quarreling;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>likewise also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29709R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29709R\"></sup>that women should adorn themselves in respectable apparel, with modesty and self-control, not with braided hair and gold or pearls or costly attire,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29710S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29710S\"></sup>but with what is proper for women who profess godliness—with good works.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Let a woman learn quietly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29711T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29711T\"></sup>with all submissiveness.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29712U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29712U\"></sup>I do not permit a woman to teach or to exercise authority over a man; rather, she is to remain quiet.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29713V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29713V\"></sup>For Adam was formed first, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29713W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29713W\"></sup>then Eve;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and Adam was not deceived, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29714X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29714X\"></sup>the woman was deceived and became a transgressor.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Yet she will be saved through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29715Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29715Y\"></sup>childbearing—if they continue in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29715Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29715Z\"></sup>faith and love and holiness, with self-control."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>The saying is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29716A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29716A\"></sup>trustworthy: If anyone aspires to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29716B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29716B\"></sup>the office of overseer, he desires a noble task.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29717C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29717C\"></sup>an overseer must be above reproach, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29717D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29717D\"></sup>the husband of one wife, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29717E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29717E\"></sup>sober-minded, self-controlled, respectable, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29717F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29717F\"></sup>hospitable, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29717G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29717G\"></sup>able to teach,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>not a drunkard, not violent but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29718H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29718H\"></sup>gentle, not quarrelsome, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29718I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29718I\"></sup>not a lover of money.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He must manage his own household well, with all dignity <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29719J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29719J\"></sup>keeping his children submissive,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>for if someone does not know how to manage his own household, how will he care for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29720K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29720K\"></sup>God's church?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He must not be a recent convert, or he may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29721L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29721L\"></sup>become puffed up with conceit and fall into the condemnation of the devil.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Moreover, he must be well thought of by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29722M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29722M\"></sup>outsiders, so that he may not fall into disgrace, into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29722N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29722N\"></sup>a snare of the devil.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29723O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29723O\"></sup>Deacons likewise must be dignified, not double-tongued, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29723P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29723P\"></sup>not addicted to much wine, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29723Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29723Q\"></sup>not greedy for dishonest gain.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29724R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29724R\"></sup>hold the mystery of the faith with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29724S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29724S\"></sup>a clear conscience.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29725T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29725T\"></sup>let them also be tested first; then let them serve as deacons if they prove themselves blameless.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29726U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29726U\"></sup>Their wives likewise must be dignified, not slanderers, but sober-minded, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29726V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29726V\"></sup>faithful in all things.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Let deacons each be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29727W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29727W\"></sup>the husband of one wife, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29727X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29727X\"></sup>managing their children and their own households well.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29728Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29728Y\"></sup>those who serve well as deacons gain a good standing for themselves and also great confidence in the faith that is in Christ Jesus.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I hope to come to you soon, but I am writing these things to you so that,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>if I delay, you may know how one ought to behave in the household of God, which is the church of the living God, a pillar and buttress of the truth.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Great indeed, we confess, is the mystery of godliness:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29731Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29731Z\"></sup>He was manifested in the flesh,vindicated by the Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29731AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29731AA\"></sup>seen by angels,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29731AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29731AB\"></sup>proclaimed among the nations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29731AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29731AC\"></sup>believed on in the world,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29731AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29731AD\"></sup>taken up in glory."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29732A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29732A\"></sup>the Spirit expressly says that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29732B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29732B\"></sup>in later times some will depart from the faith by devoting themselves to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29732C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29732C\"></sup>deceitful spirits and teachings of demons,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>through the insincerity of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29733D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29733D\"></sup>liars whose consciences are seared,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29734E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29734E\"></sup>who forbid marriage and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29734F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29734F\"></sup>require abstinence from foods <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29734G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29734G\"></sup>that God created <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29734H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29734H\"></sup>to be received with thanksgiving by those who believe and know the truth.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29735I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29735I\"></sup>everything created by God is good, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29735J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29735J\"></sup>nothing is to be rejected if it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29735K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29735K\"></sup>received with thanksgiving,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>for it is made holy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29736L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29736L\"></sup>by the word of God and prayer.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29737M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29737M\"></sup>If you put these things before the brothers, you will be a good servant of Christ Jesus, being trained in the words of the faith and of the good doctrine that you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29737N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29737N\"></sup>followed.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Have nothing to do with irreverent, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29738O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29738O\"></sup>silly myths. Rather <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29738P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29738P\"></sup>train yourself for godliness;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>for while <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29739Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29739Q\"></sup>bodily training is of some value, godliness <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29739R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29739R\"></sup>is of value in every way, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29739S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29739S\"></sup>it holds promise for the present life and also for the life to come.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The saying is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29740T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29740T\"></sup>trustworthy and deserving of full acceptance.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For to this end we toil and strive, because we have our hope set on the living God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29741U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29741U\"></sup>who is the Savior of all people, especially of those who believe.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Command and teach <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29742V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29742V\"></sup>these things.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29743W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29743W\"></sup>Let no one despise you for your youth, but set the believers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29743X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29743X\"></sup>an example in speech, in conduct, in love, in faith, in purity.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Until I come, devote yourself to the public reading of Scripture, to exhortation, to teaching.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29745Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29745Y\"></sup>Do not neglect the gift you have, which was given you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29745Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29745Z\"></sup>by prophecy when the council of elders <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29745AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29745AA\"></sup>laid their hands on you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Practice these things, immerse yourself in them, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29746AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29746AB\"></sup>all may see your progress.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29747AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29747AC\"></sup>Keep a close watch on yourself and on the teaching. Persist in this, for by so doing you will save <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29747AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29747AD\"></sup>both yourself and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29747AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29747AE\"></sup>your hearers."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29748A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29748A\"></sup>Do not rebuke an older man but encourage him as you would a father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29748B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29748B\"></sup>younger men as brothers,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>older women as mothers, younger women as sisters, in all purity.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Honor widows <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29750C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29750C\"></sup>who are truly widows.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But if a widow has children or grandchildren, let them first learn <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29751D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29751D\"></sup>to show godliness to their own household and to make some return to their parents, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29751E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29751E\"></sup>this is pleasing in the sight of God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>She <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29752F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29752F\"></sup>who is truly a widow, left all alone, has set her hope on God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29752G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29752G\"></sup>continues in supplications and prayers night and day,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29753H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29753H\"></sup>she who is self-indulgent is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29753I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29753I\"></sup>dead even while she lives.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29754J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29754J\"></sup>Command these things as well, so that they may be without reproach.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But if anyone does not provide for his relatives, and especially for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29755K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29755K\"></sup>members of his household, he has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29755L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29755L\"></sup>denied the faith and is worse than an unbeliever.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Let a widow be enrolled if she is not less than sixty years of age, having been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29756M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29756M\"></sup>the wife of one husband,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and having a reputation for good works: if she has brought up children, has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29757N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29757N\"></sup>shown hospitality, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29757O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29757O\"></sup>has washed the feet of the saints, has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29757P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29757P\"></sup>cared for the afflicted, and has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29757Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29757Q\"></sup>devoted herself to every good work.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But refuse to enroll younger widows, for when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29758R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29758R\"></sup>their passions draw them away from Christ, they desire to marry",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and so incur condemnation for having abandoned their former faith.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Besides that, they learn to be idlers, going about from house to house, and not only idlers, but also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29760S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29760S\"></sup>gossips and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29760T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29760T\"></sup>busybodies, saying what they should not.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So I would have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29761U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29761U\"></sup>younger widows marry, bear children, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29761V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29761V\"></sup>manage their households, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29761W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29761W\"></sup>give the adversary no occasion for slander.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29762X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29762X\"></sup>For some have already strayed after Satan.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>If any believing woman has relatives who are widows, let her care for them. Let the church not be burdened, so that it may care for those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29763Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29763Y\"></sup>who are truly widows.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Let the elders <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29764Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29764Z\"></sup>who rule well be considered worthy of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29764AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29764AA\"></sup>double honor, especially those who labor in preaching and teaching.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For the Scripture says, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29765AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29765AB\"></sup>“You shall not muzzle an ox when it treads out the grain,” and, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29765AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29765AC\"></sup>“The laborer deserves his wages.”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Do not admit a charge against an elder except <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29766AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29766AD\"></sup>on the evidence of two or three witnesses.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>As for those who persist in sin, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29767AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29767AE\"></sup>rebuke them in the presence of all, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29767AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29767AF\"></sup>so that the rest may stand in fear.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>In the presence of God and of Christ Jesus and of the elect angels <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29768AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29768AG\"></sup>I charge you to keep these rules without prejudging, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29768AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29768AH\"></sup>doing nothing from partiality.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29769AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29769AI\"></sup>Do not be hasty in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29769AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29769AJ\"></sup>laying on of hands, nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29769AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29769AK\"></sup>take part in the sins of others; keep yourself pure.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>(No longer drink only water, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29770AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29770AL\"></sup>use a little wine <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29770AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29770AM\"></sup>for the sake of your stomach and your frequent ailments.)",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The sins of some people are conspicuous, going before them to judgment, but the sins of others appear later.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>So also good works are conspicuous, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29772AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29772AN\"></sup>even those that are not cannot remain hidden."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29773A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29773A\"></sup>Let all who are under a yoke as bondservants regard their own masters as worthy of all honor, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29773B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29773B\"></sup>so that the name of God and the teaching may not be reviled.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Those who have believing masters must not be disrespectful on the ground that they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29774C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29774C\"></sup>brothers; rather they must serve all the better since those who benefit by their good service are believers and beloved.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29774D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29774D\"></sup>Teach and urge these things.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>If anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29775E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29775E\"></sup>teaches a different doctrine and does not agree with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29775F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29775F\"></sup>the sound words of our Lord Jesus Christ and the teaching <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29775G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29775G\"></sup>that accords with godliness,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29776H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29776H\"></sup>he is puffed up with conceit and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29776I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29776I\"></sup>understands nothing. He has an unhealthy craving for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29776J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29776J\"></sup>controversy and for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29776K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29776K\"></sup>quarrels about words, which produce envy, dissension, slander, evil suspicions,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and constant friction among people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29777L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29777L\"></sup>who are depraved in mind and deprived of the truth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29777M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29777M\"></sup>imagining that godliness is a means of gain.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29778N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29778N\"></sup>godliness <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29778O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29778O\"></sup>with contentment is great gain,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29779P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29779P\"></sup>we brought nothing into the world, and we cannot take anything out of the world.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29780Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29780Q\"></sup>if we have food and clothing, with these we will be content.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29781R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29781R\"></sup>those who desire to be rich fall into temptation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29781S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29781S\"></sup>into a snare, into many senseless and harmful desires that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29781T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29781T\"></sup>plunge people into ruin and destruction.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For the love of money is a root of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29782U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29782U\"></sup>all kinds of evils. It is through this craving that some have wandered away from the faith and pierced themselves with many pangs.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But as for you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29783V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29783V\"></sup>O man of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29783W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29783W\"></sup>flee these things. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29783X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29783X\"></sup>Pursue righteousness, godliness, faith, love, steadfastness, gentleness.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29784Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29784Y\"></sup>Fight the good fight of the faith. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29784Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29784Z\"></sup>Take hold of the eternal life <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29784AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29784AA\"></sup>to which you were called and about which you made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29784AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29784AB\"></sup>the good confession in the presence of many witnesses.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29785AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29785AC\"></sup>I charge you in the presence of God, who gives life to all things, and of Christ Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29785AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29785AD\"></sup>who in his testimony before Pontius Pilate made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29785AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29785AE\"></sup>the good confession,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>to keep the commandment unstained and free from reproach until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29786AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29786AF\"></sup>the appearing of our Lord Jesus Christ,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>which he will display <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29787AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29787AG\"></sup>at the proper time—he who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29787AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29787AH\"></sup>the blessed and only Sovereign, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29787AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29787AI\"></sup>the King of kings and Lord of lords,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29788AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29788AJ\"></sup>who alone has immortality, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29788AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29788AK\"></sup>who dwells in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29788AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29788AL\"></sup>unapproachable light, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29788AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29788AM\"></sup>whom no one has ever seen or can see. To him be honor and eternal dominion. Amen.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>As for the rich in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29789AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29789AN\"></sup>this present age, charge them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29789AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29789AO\"></sup>not to be haughty, nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29789AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29789AP\"></sup>to set their hopes on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29789AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29789AQ\"></sup>the uncertainty of riches, but on God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29789AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29789AR\"></sup>who richly provides us with everything to enjoy.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>They are to do good, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29790AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29790AS\"></sup>to be rich in good works, to be generous and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29790AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29790AT\"></sup>ready to share,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>thus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29791AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29791AU\"></sup>storing up treasure for themselves as a good foundation for the future, so that they may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29791AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29791AV\"></sup>take hold of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29791AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29791AW\"></sup>that which is truly life.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>O Timothy, guard the deposit entrusted to you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29792AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29792AX\"></sup>Avoid the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29792AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29792AY\"></sup>irreverent babble and contradictions of what is falsely called “knowledge,”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>for by professing it some have swerved from the faith.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29793AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29793AZ\"></sup>Grace be with you."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;